section.def:
1993 IGC Code (《1993年國際氣體規則》) means the 1993 edition of the International Code for the
            Construction and Equipment of Ships Carrying Liquefied Gases in Bulk published by
            IMO;

1998 IBC Code (《1998年國際化學品規則》) means the 1998 edition of the International Code for the
            Construction and Equipment of Ships Carrying Dangerous Chemicals in Bulk published by
            IMO;

BLG/Circ.13
                (《BLG/13號通函》) means the circular issued by IMO
            bearing “BLG/Circ.13” as its reference number;
